| Layer | Services |
|-------|----------|
| Data Ingestion | ADF/Synapse Pipelines, REST, SFTP, Linked Services |
| Storage | ADLS Gen2 (Delta/Parquet/CSV) |
| Compute | Synapse Spark (PySpark) |
| ETL/ELT | Notebooks + SQL |
| Modeling | Azure SQL DB + SQL DW |
| Monitoring | Log tables + Email alerts |
| Framework | Medallion Architecture |
| Incremental Loads | Watermark tracking |

